诊断，显示为甲状腺恶性肿瘤伴肝脏、脾脏、胰腺多部位淋巴结及骨转移癌，腰部、臀部、骶尾部压疮 IV 期，肿瘤相关性贫血（重度）。 目前我们已组织医疗专家对其进行全面救治，妇联、医保、民政等部门已采取相关帮扶措施。相关部门正就网友关注的其他问题进行全面调查核实。 警方回应六盘水女子患癌事件：虐待系网友误解，丈夫在家照顾 _ 进行 _ 视频 _ 六盘水"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-0332df61e916ffe13cc3973b2eada069_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "110 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/544692653"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ips6ivdnPx5V0EAMaCDgzMzI1NTU5IP+Q6JYGMAA4P0AScgk1NDQ2OTI2NTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1658574176.4178703", "card_id": "Q_544890522", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价综艺《中国说唱巅峰对决》第五期？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "86 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/544890522"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ips6ivdnPx5V0EAMaCDgzMzY5NTAwINPc7ZYGMAA4H0ATcgk1NDQ4OTA1MjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1658574176.418229", "card_id": "Q_444695125", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 755}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "孙悟空改了生死簿，阎王为什么不改回去？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f5f832798a727e66c89044ebe941b37c_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/444695125"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIps6ivdnPx5V0EAMaCDYxMDk5NzczINyerYEGMD040BFAFHIJNDQ0Njk1MTI1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style